message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs. With its exceptional features and quality, it's truly a valuable asset for anyone looking to enhance their experience. Given its worth to you, I propose a price of $140 for this product. I believe this offer strikes a balance between value and affordability, ensuring you get the best deal while allowing me to fairly compensate for my efforts and costs. I look forward to your positive response.
